    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_138868385" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/138868385" />
    <a title="Margaret" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/991805-margaret"><img alt="Margaret" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1207023483p2/991805.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/138868385?book_show_action=true">Jan 06, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Margaret" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Margaret" href="/user/show/991805-margaret">Margaret</a>
      </span>

          marked it as to-read


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780804704861" href="/book/show/30736.The_Complete_Essays_of_Montaigne">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/991805-margaret?shelf=will-get-back-to-later">will-get-back-to-later</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer138868385" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14926276457498760373">This is a book I am always reading and have been for years. I rarely read more than an essay at any given time, but what riches Montaigne offers. I&apos;m currently rereading as I read Sarah Bakewell&apos;s How to Live: A Life of Montaigne.</span>
  <span id="freeText14926276457498760373" style="display:none">This is a book I am always reading and have been for years. I rarely read more than an essay at any given time, but what riches Montaigne offers. I'm currently rereading as I read Sarah Bakewell's How to Live: A Life of Montaigne.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14926276457498760373" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


