        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer20275163" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12411324154685484602">Going into these essays, I felt, fundamentally, that reading Montaigne was more of an intellectual obligation than something that I actually might enjoy. It was pleasant to be proven wrong. While not life-changing, these are the sorts of solid, liberal ideas that I&apos;m glad could be formulated as early as the Renaissance, and it&apos;s extremely nice to see that someone could write something that would so resonate with modern audiences... even jaded college kids like myself.</span>
  <span id="freeText12411324154685484602" style="display:none">Going into these essays, I felt, fundamentally, that reading Montaigne was more of an intellectual obligation than something that I actually might enjoy. It was pleasant to be proven wrong. While not life-changing, these are the sorts of solid, liberal ideas that I'm glad could be formulated as early as the Renaissance, and it's extremely nice to see that someone could write something that would so resonate with modern audiences... even jaded college kids like myself.</span>
